<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Confidence" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Confidence,</orth> 1) trust: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.4.6" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 4, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.4.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 4, 31</bibl>.<lb />2) assurance, security: <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.172" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.414" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 414</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.167" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 167</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.6.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 6, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 2, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.4.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 4, 121</bibl>. <cit><quote>they take it already upon their c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 10</bibl></cit> (Qq <emph>salvation</emph>). <cit><quote>in all c., he's not for Rhodes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 31</bibl></cit>.
<lb />Misapplied for <cit><quote>conference:</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.172" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 4, 172</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 5, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.4.133" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom II, 4, 133</bibl>.
